      *@  기준년월일＝자료기준일자　일치　확인
           PERFORM  S3100-BASEYMD-CHK-RTN
              THRU  S3100-BASEYMD-CHK-EXT

           PERFORM  UNTIL  IN-EOF-Y
      *       해외은행외화타점예치금(1040101020001) 대상
      *       부코핀(BBUKIDJAXXX), 프라삭(CZNBKHPPXXX),
      *       미얀마(CZNBMMMYXXX), 중국(CZNBCNBJXXX)
               IF  IN-TIACC-CD  = '1040101020001' AND
                   IN-DEPO(1:8) = ('BBUKIDJA' OR 'CZNBKHPP' OR
                                   'CZNBMMMY' OR 'CZNBCNBJ')
                   PERFORM  S3300-KJLR019-INSERT-RTN
