      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
       S3300-KJLR019-INSERT-RTN.

           INITIALIZE                   TRJLR019-REC

      *    그룹회사코드
           MOVE  WK-H-I-GROUP-CO-CD
             TO  RJLR019-GROUP-CO-CD

190808*    기준년월일(작업기준일)
