             TO  RJLR019-CNCYCD

      *    거래은행BIC코드(DEPO CODE)
           MOVE  IN-DEPO
             TO  RJLR019-TRAN-BNK-BIC

      *    통합계정과목코드
           MOVE  IN-TIACC-CD
             TO  RJLR019-INTGRA-TIACC-CD

