             TO  RJLR019-WONC-AUC

      *@1 외화타점예치계좌기본수보 전영업일 등록정보 조회
           PERFORM  S3310-KJLR019-SELECT-RTN
              THRU  S3310-KJLR019-SELECT-EXT

      *   고객식별자
           MOVE  WK-KB-PIN
             TO  RJLR019-CUST-IDNFR
      *   등록직원번호
           MOVE  WK-REGI-EMPID
             TO  RJLR019-REGI-EMPID
      *   등록일시
           MOVE  WK-REGI-YMS
             TO  RJLR019-REGI-YMS

      *    DBIO CALL
           #DYDBIO  INSERT-CMD-Y TKJLR019-PK TRJLR019-REC

           EVALUATE  TRUE
               WHEN  COND-DBIO-OK
                     ADD   CO-NUM-1    TO  WK-AC-INSERT-CNT
               WHEN  OTHER
                     MOVE 'KJLR019'    TO  XZUGEROR-I-TBL-ID
